         <h3 style="margin-top: 60px;">CO-INVESTORS</h3>

           <p1 style="margin-left: 30px;">We look to acquire a controlling interest, and invest our own capital in each deal.</p1>

           <p1 style="margin-left: 30px;">We originate, sponsor, and syndicate the deal by adding the right investment partners as co-investors. Our co-investors include family offices and institutional investors. We present them with completed term sheets under exclusivity, they determine the fit, and and then we jointly structure the transaction to preserve the core elements of the negotiated terms while presenting the best opportunity for business success and compelling returns.</p1>

           <h3 style="margin-top: 60px;">OPPORTUNISTIC, HANDS-ON AND COLLABORATIVE</h3>

           <p1 style="margin-left: 30px;">We are not restricted by an investment charter; thus, we are free to pursue deals where we believe we can add significant value regardless of location, industry or size. We are also able to custom fit the right deal to the right co-investor(s).</p1>

           <p1 style="margin-left: 30px;">We look for superior management teams and partner with them to tighten strategic plans, improve execution, and accelerate growth.</p1>

           <p1 style="margin-left: 30px;">We take board seats in each deal to help direct and drive business performance.</p1>


